-- Dubai Electricity Awards $142 Million in Contracts to Ansaldo Energia, ABB
-- Ayesha Daya
-- 2010-07-12T04:36:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/dubai-electricity-awards-142-million-in-contracts-to-ansaldo-energia-abb.html

          
          
             Dubai Electricity and Water
Authority awarded 522 million dirhams ($142 million) in
contracts to expand its facilities.  
 Ansaldo Energia SpA, a unit of Finmeccanica SpA, won a 450
million-dirham contract to provide parts and services for 10
years at Jebel Ali power station, Dubai Electricity said in an
e-mailed statement today. ABB Ltd. won contracts valued at 70
million dirhams, and Areva received orders worth 2.5 million
dirhams, according to the statement.  
